'From Squeak3.7alpha of 11 September 2003 [latest update: #5707] on 16 February 2004 at 7:00:06 pm'!"Change Set:		tests-reorganize-mdDate:			16 February 2004Author:			Marcus DenkerThe unit-test from the Tests package have been added to the image.This changeset now renames all Tests-* categories to be *-Tests.Rational: When breaking stuff out (e.g. make a MC package Network-Url)then we sure want the tests be part of that, not continue to bepart of the image. Some Tests* categories remain, e.g. Tests-KCP and Tests-Bugz."!"Postscript:"Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Collections-Support' toBe: 'Collections-Support-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Kernel-Classes' toBe: 'Kernel-Classes-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Kernel-Magnitudes' toBe: 'Kernel-Magnitudes-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Morphic-Widgets' toBe: 'Morphic-Widgets-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Collections-Streams' toBe: 'Collections-Streams-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Kernel-Methods' toBe: 'Kernel-Methods-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Collections-Arrayed' toBe: 'Collections-Arrayed-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Morphic-Demo' toBe: 'Morphic-Demo-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Graphics-Primitives' toBe: 'Graphics-Primitives-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Kernel-Objects' toBe: 'Kernel-Objects-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Collections-Text' toBe: 'Collections-Text-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Exceptions' toBe: 'Exceptions-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Kernel-Processes' toBe: 'Kernel-Processes-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Collections-Unordered' toBe: 'Collections-Unordered-Tests'.Smalltalk organization renameCategory: 'Tests-Tools-FileList' toBe: 'Tools-FileList-Tests'.Sma